name: FPS Tower Denense Set in the Near Future that is very Unfinished
name_original: FPS Tower Denense Set in the Near Future that is very Unfinished
description: This is a game that is super unfinished and pointless. It is a parody of a near future FPS game (or Call of Duty as of BO2). It sucks, I know. I couldn't get it done. Consider this a pre-alpha demo for a game that will never be finished. Textures from CGtextures. Models made by me. Please don't rate so horribly, I know it sucks. At least rate this for self awarness!
